  "Format string for rendering statuses.
Ex. \"%i %s,  %@:\\n%FILL{  %t // from %f%L%r%R}\n \"

Items:
 %s - screen_name
 %S - name
 %i - profile_image
 %d - description
 %l - location
 %L - \" [location]\"
 %r - \" sent to user\" (use on direct_messages{,_sent})
 %r - \" in reply to user\" (use on other standard timeline)
